    "Several studies utilize this method to perform sentiment analysis on news reports with decent accuracy scores (39).",
    "One study constructed a sentiment dictionary to understand and identify the emotional distribution of a news article.",
    "This algorithm often forms the baseline for more complex models to be built on top of it.",
    "To tackle more complex datasets with longer texts, a different approach rooted in machine learning is required.",
    "The sentences are initially preprocessed through either the Term Frequency -Inverse Document Frequency algorithm (41), or the Bag of Words algorithm."
